  "text": "1e3 Furthermore, PVR management is costly in patient time and healthcare resources. [CITATION_1] Numerous adjunctive medications have been evaluated in clinical trials, 4e12 yet no effective and safe adjunct has gained widespread acceptance.",
  "correct_citation": {
